ProductName: Truvia Natural Sweetener, 400 Count (Pack of 1)
ProductSubCategory: Truvia Natural Sweetener, 400 Count (Pack of 1)
Description: Sweetness is meant to be enjoyed. That's why Truvia created products meant to reduce sugar, not taste. The clean, sweet flavor contained in Truvia Natural Sweetener packets comes from nature in the form of the stevia leaf. Leaves don't dissolve well in beverages or baked goods, so we extract the sweetness from the stevia leaf. Because stevia leaf extract is 200x sweeter than sugar, we balance the sweetness with erythritol, a sweetener produced by fermentation. Erythritol is also found in fruits like grapes and pears. This gives you the white crystals you're used to without the calories. This 400-count box can be stashed at home, at work or a few packets can be thrown in your bag for on-the-go sweetness.

ProductName: Califia Farms® Organic Oatmilk
ProductSubCategory: Califia Farms® Organic Oatmilk

Organic Oatmilk pure and simple. We expertly blend just water, oats and sea salt to create this dairy-free deliciousness in its purest plant-based form. No oils and no gums. NO OILS, NO GUMS: Califia Organic Oatmilk is made with just three simple ingredients without oils or gums. Just shake it up and enjoy!

THREE SIMPLE INGREDIENTS: Purified water, organic oats, and sea salt. This is plant-based dairy-free goodness in its purest form. No oils and no gums. It’s deliciously simple.
PLANT-BASED: Califia Farms® products are made with plant-based ingredients to acheive irresistible goodness in every way––taste, versatility, and all the benefits of being dairy-free.
DON'T FORGET TO SHAKE: Settling is natural in high-quality plant-based milks so remember to shake well!

Description:
With the velvety texture and creaminess of Califia Farms Extra Creamy Oatmilk, you won’t miss dairy milk again.It’s the milkiest of all the plant milks. Oats make a perfectly smooth dairy-free milk with a velvety texture and a subtle sweetness that doesn’t overpower. EASY SWAP FROM DAIRY: Extra Creamy Oatmilk makes a smooth swap from dairy with its rich and creamy texture, neutral flavor, and incredible versatility. With this oat milk in your life, you won't miss dairy milk again
EXCELLENT SOURCE OF CALCIUM: Extra Creamy Oatmilk is an excellent source of calcium, vitamin A and vitamin D. Plus it's made with gluten-free oats
SIMPLE PLANT-BASED INGREDIENTS: Califia Farms oat milks are made with plant-based, dairy-free ingredients that are Non-GMO Certified, Glyphosate free, Kosher, vegan, and free from carrageenan. Made with gluten-free oats
USE FOR COOKING & BAKING: Extra Creamy Oatmilk is the perfect plant-based milk for cooking, baking, everything-making! Plus it's delicious in all the obvious ways: pour over cereal, add to coffee, blend into smoothies, or sip straight from the glass
